===message:I agree, Chris.  On the whole, I think these movements were more beneficial than harmful.  I also think these movements were inevitable.  Since the beginning of mankind, conflict has existed among different groups of people.  For anyone to think that these movements could have been avoided would be incredulous.  Conflict between humans will always exist in some form or another.  Peace is a wonderful concept, but not a realistic one.  Controversy and conflict is necessary for our cultures and societies to evolve.  
